</section>
<section class="Sh">
<h1 class="Sh" id="BUGS"><a class="permalink" href="#BUGS">BUGS</a></h1>
<code class="Nm">tpctl</code> isn't available on all ports because it requires a
  display device which provides the &#x2018;hpcfb&#x2019; interface.
</section>
